title: Pajaro Street Bar and Grill
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A community restaurant/bar with a variety of vegan choices labeled, as well as a few other dishes that can be made vegan. Try the veggie pie. Pesto is vegan. Gluten free menu available. Has a full bar with vegan cocktails, board games, televisions and an espresso bar. Live music every Friday night. Atmosphere is cozy, charming, with soft lights.
